{
  "stem": "15197.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even I didn't realize that it really is that people-- whole cities and towns are being wiped out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I thought that it is in camps, in the beginning, in settlements in other ghettos, in other cities.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was the main thought of the majority of the people in the Warsaw ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In-- in the Warsaw ghetto people also thought that Warsaw is the capitol and it's open for the whole world and there are embassies.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And how can they do even the same thing in such a big city with so many Jews, a half a million Jews in the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What they are doing in a small town?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So people didn't believe that it's really going, being deported to nowhere, or being killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Who was the underground leadership at the time?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The leadership in the ghetto was the Jewish council, the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the underground leadership was in the hand of the young people, as I said, of the youth organization.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they formed the so-called fighter's organization.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was in 1942.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Deportation started the 22nd of July, 1942.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then representative of youth organizations got together and they-- something has to be done.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, really, I would say in October, 1942, the organization came to life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "An understanding came that some actions in preparing the youth if another deportation starts that their response should be in an organized way.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't have any arms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I belonged to the first group of the so-called fighter's organization.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't have any arms at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a need to get arm.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a need to prepare ourself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in December, 1942, they turned to me-- it was the Bund, the third group.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
